English (EN): Do you want to liquidate your entire position?

Korean (KO): 가능 수량이 아닙니다. 구매금액과 가능금액을 확인하십시오.
English (EN): This is not the possible quantity. Please check the Qty and Price.
There are no orders to cancel.

Korean (KO): [충전불가] 포지션에 체결된 주문을 모두 청산 후 시도하세요.
English (EN): [Unable to recharge] Please try again after liquidating all orders concluded in the position.
